 200 | ATR% regime (0-200) |\n| **Institutional Flow** | 150 | T86 foreign/trust flow (0-75 + 0-75) |\n| **Structure Score** | 150 | Fib 618 proximity (0-80), pivot quality (0-70) |\n| **TOTAL** | **1000** | |\n\n### 2.2 Signal Thresholds\n\n| Score | Signal | Position Size | Action |\n|-------|--------|---------------|--------|\n| **700-1000** | **APPROVE** | 5% of portfolio | Enter full size |\n| **500-699** | **CAUTION** | 2.5% of portfolio | Enter half size |\n| **350-499** | **WATCH** | 1% | Small probe, tight stop |\n| **< 350** | **REJECT** | 0% | Skip |\n\n### 2.3 Score Calibration (v3.1 Backtest Results)\n\n| Component | Default Weight | Calibrated | Notes |\n|-----------|---------------|-----------|-------|\n| Momentum | 30% | **35%** | Most predictive in backtest |\n| Trend | 25% | **25%** | Stable |\n| ATR | 20% | **15%** | Reduced — ATR stops were losers |\n| Institutional | 10% | **10%** | T86 data integration pending |\n| Structure | 15% | **15%** | Stable |\n\n---\n\n## 3. Entry Rules\n\n### 3.1 Entry Conditions (ALL must be true)\n\n```\n✅ Daily EMA tunnel aligned:\n   Daily EMA144 > Daily EMA169  AND  Price > Daily EMA144\n\n✅ Hourly EMA crossover:\n   Hourly EMA144 crosses above Hourly EMA169 (within last 4 hours)\n\n✅ KDJ J-cross triggered:\n   J-line crosses above K and D simultaneously (within last 4 hours)\n\n✅ Fib 618 structure:\n   Price within ±3% of identified Fib 618 support pivot\n\n✅ RSI condition:\n   Stock RSI (14) < 65 (tightened from <70)\n\n✅ Score threshold:\n   Score >= 350 (raised from 200)\n\n✅ VIX filter (market context):\n   VIX < 25 (no extreme panic)\n```\n\n### 3.2 Entry Steps\n\n1. **Daily Filter Check** (09:30 ET)\n   - Scan universe, filter by Daily EMA alignment\n   - Identify candidates passing environment filter\n\n2. **Hourly Trigger Monitoring** (every hour)\n   - Watch for EMA 144/169 crossover on hourly chart\n   - Confirm with KDJ J-cross\n\n3. **Structure Validation**\n   - Verify price near Fib 618 support\n  